# Multi-line class LST fixture.
# In real PCGen data files a single CLASS entity is commonly split across two or
# more lines when the line would otherwise exceed the column limit.  All lines
# sharing the same CLASS:Name head are logically one entity.
#
# Pattern from spycraft_classes.lst (Spycraft 2.0 OGL, Patrick Kapera et al.):
#   CLASS:Faceman	HD:10	TYPE:Base.PC	MAXLEVEL:20	...
#   CLASS:Faceman	STARTSKILLPTS:6	CSKILL:Bluff|...
#
# We use synthetic data that exercises the same grammar without reproducing
# proprietary stat values.
CLASS:Faceman	HITDIE:10	TYPE:Base.PC	MAXLEVEL:20	ABB:Fcm	SOURCEPAGE:42
CLASS:Faceman	STARTSKILLPTS:6	CSKILL:Bluff|Diplomacy|Disguise
